casebody.head_matter:
Jamal Adeen AZEEZ, petitioner,
v.
WEST VIRGINIA, et al.
No. 16-9085.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 26, 2017.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Appeals of West Virginia dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
